(253, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>最热门的</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/ultimate-tinymce/''>Ultimate TinyMCE</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=ultimate-tinymce&amp;_wpnonce=94b04279a6&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Ultimate TinyMCE''>安装</a>)</span>\n<p>Description: Beef up your visual tinymce editor with a plethora of advanced options.</p>\n<h4>最新插件</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/geeklist-widget/''>Geeklist Widget</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=geeklist-widget&amp;_wpnonce=8926dcb26f&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Geeklist Widget''>安装</a>)</span>\n<p>Simple sidebar widget that lists your latest Geeklist activities.</p>\n', 'no'),
